    <title>Nextcloud</title>
    <link href="https://smaxad47.github.io/wiki/%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/nextcloud-snap/"/>
    <id>https://smaxad47.github.io/wiki/服务器/nextcloud-snap/</id>
    <published>2019-07-12T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-13T02:06:12.356Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo snap install nextcloud</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>登录并完成安装</p><h1 id="将存储位置挪到外部硬盘"><a href="#将存储位置挪到外部硬盘" class="headerlink" title="将存储位置挪到外部硬盘"></a>将存储位置挪到外部硬盘</h1><ol><li><p>挂载EXT4硬盘，如<code>/media/name/XXXDATA</code></p></li><li><p>可以在里面新建一个文件夹用来存放就可以不用看到<code>lost&amp;found</code>了，如<code>/media/name/XXXDATA/mydata</code></p></li><li><p>将nextcloud设置为可移动媒体:<code>sudo snap connect nextcloud:removable-media</code></p></li><li><p>修改默认nextcloud默认储存位置<code>sudo nvim /var/snap/nextcloud/current/nextcloud/config/config.php</code><br>修改内容:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">原内容:</span><br><span class="line">&apos;datadirectory&apos; =&gt; &apos;/var/snap/nextcloud/common/nextcloud/data&apos;</span><br><span class="line">改为:</span><br><span class="line">&apos;datadirectory&apos; =&gt; &apos;/media/name/XXXDATA/mydata&apos;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>关闭nextcloud,<code>sudo snap disable nextcloud</code><br>移动数据目录<code>sudo cp -r /var/snap/nextcloud/common/nextcloud/data/. /media/name/XXXDATA/mydata</code></p></li><li><p>打开nextcloud，<code>sudo snap enable nextcloud</code></p></li><li><p>可能会遇到的问题，没有权限或者权限太开放，将mydata的所有者改为root:<code>sudo chown root:root mydata</code></p></li></ol><h1 id="添加可信任域名"><a href="#添加可信任域名" class="headerlink" title="添加可信任域名"></a>添加可信任域名</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">array (</span><br><span class="line">    0 =&gt; &apos;192.168.1.100&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">    1 =&gt; &apos;domain&apos;</span><br><span class="line">  )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
