  <entry>
    <title>Nextcloud内网穿透</title>
    <link href="https://smaxad47.github.io/wiki/%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/nextcloud-caddy-frp/"/>
    <id>https://smaxad47.github.io/wiki/服务器/nextcloud-caddy-frp/</id>
    <published>2019-07-12T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-15T01:14:05.302Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h1><p>安装参考<br><a href="/wiki/服务器/Caddy">Caddy</a><br><a href="/wiki/服务器/FRP">FRP</a><br><a href="/wiki/服务器/nextcloud-snap">Nextcloud</a></p><h1 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h1><h2 id="Caddy"><a href="#Caddy" class="headerlink" title="Caddy"></a>Caddy</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">domain &#123;</span><br><span class="line">   proxy / localhost:porta &#123;</span><br><span class="line">   transparent</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>transparent</em>等价于</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">header_upstream Host &#123;host&#125;</span><br><span class="line">header_upstream X-Real-IP &#123;remote&#125;</span><br><span class="line">header_upstream X-Forwarded-For &#123;remote&#125;</span><br><span class="line">header_upstream X-Forwarded-Proto &#123;scheme&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>备注:</em>port为frp中vhost_http_port设置的端口</p><h2 id="FRP"><a href="#FRP" class="headerlink" title="FRP"></a>FRP</h2><p><em>服务端</em>配置:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[common]</span><br><span class="line">#自选frp通信端口，客户端和服务端保持一致</span><br><span class="line">bind_port = port</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 设定超时时间，可选</span><br><span class="line">authentication_timeout = 900</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># FRP后台地址和帐号密码，可选</span><br><span class="line">dashboard_port = portb</span><br><span class="line">dashboard_user = account</span><br><span class="line">dashboard_pwd = passwd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 访问内网网站的端口地址</span><br><span class="line">vhost_http_port = porta</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 访问端口的范围</span><br><span class="line">privilege_mode = true</span><br><span class="line">privilege_token = passwdx</span><br><span class="line">privilege_allow_ports = portx-porty</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>客户端</em>配置:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[common]</span><br><span class="line"># 和服务端保持一致</span><br><span class="line">server_addr = server_ip</span><br><span class="line">server_port = port</span><br><span class="line">privilege_token = passwdx</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[web]</span><br><span class="line">privilege_mode = true</span><br><span class="line">type = http</span><br><span class="line">local_port = 80</span><br><span class="line">custom_domains = domain</span><br><span class="line"># 这是加密</span><br><span class="line">use_encryption = true</span><br><span class="line"># 这是压缩</span><br><span class="line">use_compression = true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="HTTPS"><a href="#HTTPS" class="headerlink" title="HTTPS"></a>HTTPS</h1><p>用FRP穿透HTTP 和 HTTPS 80 443端口<br>用sudo nextcloud.enable-https lets-encrypt获取证书</p><p>由于Caddy并不支持<code>proxy_ssl_server_name</code><br>直接使用<a href="https://domain:port" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://domain:port</a> 来访问</p><p>FRP 配置如下:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">FRP 配置如下:</span><br><span class="line">server:</span><br><span class="line">[common]</span><br><span class="line">bind_port = porta</span><br><span class="line">vhost_https_port = portb</span><br><span class="line">authentication_timeout = 900</span><br><span class="line">token = xxxxxxxx</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">client:</span><br><span class="line">[common]</span><br><span class="line">server_addr = server_ip</span><br><span class="line">server_port = porta</span><br><span class="line">token = xxxxxxxx</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[web443]</span><br><span class="line">type = https</span><br><span class="line">local_ip = 127.0.0.1</span><br><span class="line">local_port = 443</span><br><span class="line">custom_domains = domain</span><br><span class="line">use_encryption = true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[web6800]</span><br><span class="line">type = https</span><br><span class="line">local_ip = 127.0.0.1</span><br><span class="line">local_port = 6800</span><br><span class="line">custom_domains = domain</span><br><span class="line">use_encryption = true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
