  <entry>
    <title>Caddy</title>
    <link href="https://smaxad47.github.io/wiki/%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/Caddy/"/>
    <id>https://smaxad47.github.io/wiki/服务器/Caddy/</id>
    <published>2019-07-12T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-13T08:11:45.969Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h1><p>用逗的脚本</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget -N --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ToyoDAdoubi/doubi/master/caddy_install.sh &amp;&amp; chmod +x caddy_install.sh &amp;&amp; bash caddy_install.sh</span><br><span class="line"> # 安装插件：</span><br><span class="line"> bash caddy_install.sh xxx,xxx</span><br><span class="line">  # 例如同时安装 http.filemanager 和 http.webdav插件：</span><br><span class="line">  bash caddy_install.sh http.filemanager,http.webdav</span><br><span class="line">  # 插件和Caddy是集成在一起的(单个二进制文件)，多个插件必须同时安装。</span><br><span class="line"># 卸载命令：</span><br><span class="line">wget -N --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ToyoDAdoubi/doubi/master/caddy_install.sh &amp;&amp; chmod +x caddy_install.sh &amp;&amp; caddy_install.sh uninstall</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h1><p>创建配置文件<code>/usr/local/caddy/Caddyfile</code><br>自动申请证书位置<code>/.caddy/acme/acme-v01.api.letsencrypt.org/sites/xxx.xxx(域名)/</code></p>]]></content>
    
